    ðŸ”¹ `chattr -a filename` --> ðŸš« Removes the "append-only" attribute from the file.
    ðŸ”¹ `chattr +A filename` --> â° Does not update the file's access time, for optimization.
    ðŸ”¹ `chattr -R`         --> ðŸ”„ Operates recursively on all files and directories within a directory.

